{"type": "article", "id": 18730, "title": "填充口袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-09T07:10:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144637fSIzENATPo0xmLsG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些牛皮纸做的口袋可以填充空气或者缓冲材料，是专门用来放在包裹里填充多余的空间。它最重要的优势是可以重复利用，每一个口袋都带有伸缩扣，也可以将它卷在里面，在一定程度上改变口袋的体积以适应不同的需要。如果投入使用，其实可以避免不必要的浪费。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144635fvM3FnpWdsmRy61D.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144636XnVOaYKEU4zhjgly.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144636c2x9BaPKoS5lMYsJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.99333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144637talMVfXkSevmxw4z.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}